|CKBBrew Acid: The Necessary Bad Idea|000

Syntax: brewacid

At Rank 2, Volatility 1, and Alchemy 25, prepare one owner-bound acid flask.
Cook Ash consumes that flask and all relevant ash to make a combat stimulant.
Only one uncooked flask may be carried at a time. It lasts two hours and
can instead be thrown for modest acid damage.

Throw it with 'throw acid flask at <target>'. While fighting, 'throw acid
flask' uses your current foe. Throwing engages combat, consumes the flask,
and splashes one fifth of the dealt damage back onto you.
